content: Hello, this is Sarah calling from Ali's Organization. I'm calling to collect some information for your upcoming Initial Consultation with Dr. Jane Smith on 07/25/2025 06:38 PM. Is this a good time to talk for a few minutes?

Great! Let me ask you a few questions to help prepare for your appointment.

First, Ali Raza, what is your chief complaint today?
I have, you know, a back issue since attending.
Okay, I understand you're experiencing a back issue. Could you please elaborate on what kind of back issue you're having?
